title: fanoutqa: List the films directed by the director with the second highest career film gross worldwide and provide the budget for each film in USD. (98ced84a1a9df028)

chat_history.content: List the films directed by the director with the second highest career film gross worldwide and provide the budget for each film in USD.

I assume you mean the director with the second highest career film gross worldwide. Here is a list of films directed by Steven Spielberg:

1. *E.T. The Extra-Terrestrial (1982)* - $13 million budget
2. *Jaws (1975)* - $7-9 million budget
3. *Jurassic Park (1993)* - $63 million budget
4. *Saving Private Ryan (1998)* - $70 million budget
5. *Indiana Jones and the Raiders of the Lost Ark (1981)* - $18 million budget
6. *Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom (1984)* - $28 million budget
7. *Close Encounters of the Third Kind (1977)* - $19.5 million budget
8. *Jurassic Park: The Lost World (1997)* - $73 million budget
9. *Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade (1989)* - $48 million budget
10. *War of the Worlds (2005)* - $132 million budget

Note: It is difficult to confirm the exact budget for some of these films, as figures can vary depending on the source.
